name: #56 JUST A PIG – STARVATION
description:
Special Edition.

Just a pig brings in this piece a reflection, what are you doing to help your neighbor, when they are starving in the world and we don't know it?

Reflect, Help, and Be Better. 


"JUST A PIG" is a fun collection with 100 pieces, Created by Tiagobatista20 and designed by ZEBRA. Brazilian artist.
